# Privacy Policy — Expat Weather

**Last Updated: March 4, 2026**

## Overview

Expat Weather ("the App") is developed by Michael Cooke. This Privacy Policy explains how the App handles your information.

## Information We Collect

**We do not collect any personal data.**

The App does not require an account, does not track you, and does not collect analytics. Your saved cities, home location preference, and app settings are stored locally on your device using standard iOS storage and are never transmitted to our servers.

## Weather Data

The App retrieves weather data from OpenWeather (openweathermap.org) using the geographic coordinates of cities you search for or save. These API requests include latitude and longitude coordinates only — no personal identifiers are sent. Please refer to OpenWeather's privacy policy for information on how they handle API requests: https://openweather.co.uk/privacy-policy

## Location Services

If you choose to use the "Use My Current Location" feature, the App requests your device's location through Apple's standard location services. This location data is used solely to determine your current city for weather display. Your location is sent to OpenWeather's geocoding API to resolve the city name and is not stored on any server we operate.

You can deny location access and the App will function fully — simply search for your city manually.

## Subscriptions

If you subscribe to Expat Weather Pro, your payment is processed entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not have access to your payment information, Apple ID, or billing details. Subscription management is handled through your Apple ID settings.

## Third-Party Services

The App uses the following third-party services:

- **OpenWeather API** — for weather data, forecasts, and alerts
- **Apple StoreKit** — for subscription management

No advertising networks, analytics platforms, or tracking services are used.

## Data Storage

All app data (saved cities, preferences, settings) is stored locally on your device. If you delete the App, all local data is removed.

## Children's Privacy

The App does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13. The App contains no user-generated content, social features, or data collection mechanisms.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page.

